Welcome to EnTrance - the gateway to a new you. 

One of the greatest new resources of SELF HELP AND PERSONAL DEVELOPMENT AUDIO available on the entire Internet! 

Produced by industry professionals in high end Central London recording studios. We all experience the day to day strain of life at some point in our lives. 

Guided hypnosis/meditation can help take you to the next chapter in your life. Relaxing and releasing you from the struggles you are currently going through. 

Hypnosis is when a therapist puts you into a trance. 

Meditation is when you put yourself into a trance. Trance is a completely natural state of relaxation, where positive suggestions will be accepted by our subconscious minds.

Further information and contact for personal sessions can be found at: http://www.EnTrance.org.uk
